# UI Package Exports

This document explains the export structure of the `@boilerplate/ui` package.

## Export Structure

The package provides both individual component exports and categorized exports.

### Individual Component Exports

Direct access to specific components:

```tsx
import { Button } from '@boilerplate/ui/button'
import { Input } from '@boilerplate/ui/input'
import { Dialog } from '@boilerplate/ui/dialog'
```

### Categorized Exports

Access to all components in a category:

```tsx
import { Button, Card, Accordion } from '@boilerplate/ui/interactive'
import { Input, Select, Checkbox } from '@boilerplate/ui/data-entry'
import { Dialog, Popover, Tooltip } from '@boilerplate/ui/overlays'
```

