### Category Exports

- `./data-entry` - Form inputs and data collection
- `./interactive` - User interaction components
- `./layout` - Structure and organization
- `./navigation` - Site navigation and menus
- `./data-display` - Information presentation
- `./date-time` - Date and time functionality
- `./feedback` - User feedback and status
- `./overlays` - Components above other content
- `./typography` - Text display components

### Utility Exports

- `./utils` - Utility functions
- `./globals.css` - Global styles
- `./postcss.config` - PostCSS configuration

## Usage Examples

### Importing Individual Components

```tsx
import { Button, buttonVariants } from '@boilerplate/ui/button'
import { Input } from '@boilerplate/ui/input'
import { Dialog, DialogContent, DialogTrigger } from '@boilerplate/ui/dialog'
```

### Importing from Categories

```tsx
// Interactive components
import { Button, Card, Accordion } from '@boilerplate/ui/interactive'

// Form components
import { Input, Select, Checkbox, Switch } from '@boilerplate/ui/data-entry'

// Overlay components
import { Dialog, Popover, Tooltip, HoverCard } from '@boilerplate/ui/overlays'

// Feedback components
import { Alert, Badge, Skeleton, Progress } from '@boilerplate/ui/feedback'
```

### Importing Utilities

```tsx
import { cn } from '@boilerplate/ui/utils'
import '@boilerplate/ui/globals.css'
```
